dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Lake Hughes and Del Sur quadrangles, Los Angeles County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Del Sur - Lake Hughes quadrangle
Lake Hughes and Del Sur maps
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared in cooperation with the California Department of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and the U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes 2 col. cross sections, quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
